Package: uperf-linux
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Depends: libglib2.0-0 (>= 2.0), libdbus-1-3 (>= 1.0), libjson-c5 (>= 0.12), libsystemd0 (>= 209)
Maintainer: code002-2 <hiez832670@gmail.com>
Description: Userspace performance scheduler for Linux ARM64 gaming devices
 uperf-linux is a userspace CPU/GPU scheduler for Linux ARM64 gaming
 devices. It monitors touch input, thermal zones, and CPU load to
 dynamically adjust scheduling parameters for optimal gaming performance.
 .
 This package includes:
  - uperf-linux: the background daemon
  - uperfctl: CLI control tool
  - uperf-wizard: hardware detection and config generator
